    <h3>Fee & Payment Policy</h3>
    <p>Fees: R900 (children without pampers), R1000 (children wearing pampers). Registration fee: R400 for new children. December fees must be paid in October. Concert fee and graduation fee are compulsory and non-refundable. Late payments: R100 penalty.</p>
